  <summary date="2024-02-07T16:59:53Z" status="Introduced in House">Mandating the Abolition of a Threat to Consumer Happiness Act or the MATCH Act 

This bill implements a hiring freeze at the Consumer Financial Protection Bureau. Further, new positions may not be established and employees and officers may not be assigned new duties or transferred to other duty stations.</summary>
